{
  "name": "Heroes Never Die",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 18th level, your allies have no fear of death in your presence. As a reaction, if another creature within 60 feet of you that you can see would drop to 0 hit points as a result of taking damage, you can cause it to drop to 1 hit point instead. You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Wisdom modifier (a minimum of once), and you regain all expended uses of it when you finish a long rest.</p>",
